label: 371. Booklet used to improve penmanship -- 1893-1896
description: Booklet with poetry, psalms, and letters copied probably to improve penmanship (some letters found in collection).  Dated entries range from 1893-1896.  Some signed Marie Hayne Heyward.  84p.
